    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试着走出自己的公寓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/6951f7887f45b8f4b4dd741d05944cdd.poster.avif?t=1770820455\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/6951f7887f45b8f4b4dd741d05944cdd.webm?t=1770820455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/6951f7887f45b8f4b4dd741d05944cdd.mp4?t=1770820455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超现实的巨大迷宫</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在收到失踪室友的神秘语音邮件后，你的公寓就变成了一个超现实的迷宫。在他的声音和定制的复古游戏机的指引下，踏上解密之旅吧，你的家已经变成了一个神秘的迷宫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是要小心。你越是深入其他现实世界，就越难找到回去的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/f02b3626bb03435f3f08b192b79a6908.poster.avif?t=1770820455\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/f02b3626bb03435f3f08b192b79a6908.webm?t=1770820455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/f02b3626bb03435f3f08b192b79a6908.mp4?t=1770820455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>身临其境、令人费解的逃脱游戏</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索嵌套公寓 - 揭开新房间的神秘面纱，寻找线索，并设法弄清相互连接的门和走廊，让您在未知的世界里越走越远。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古通行证 - 使用神秘的 GameLeaf 完成具有挑战性的关卡，收集隐藏物品，解锁新的探索区域。每一个游戏都是一块拼图，让你更接近揭开法尔失踪背后的真相。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/ed7fa6377584bfc253a55647b8aa8ccb.poster.avif?t=1770820455\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/ed7fa6377584bfc253a55647b8aa8ccb.webm?t=1770820455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212390/extras/ed7fa6377584bfc253a55647b8aa8ccb.mp4?t=1770820455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装置清单 - 密切关注细节：从相框到看似无关的家具，您所看到的一切都可能是解开谜题的线索。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实验是关键--与场景互动，拾取物品，将它们组合起来。你的公寓世界充满了惊喜，你需要跳出框框来思考才能取得进展。但是，当你揭开 Fael 神秘失踪的面纱时，你会开始质疑现实本身的本质。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
